      "role": "user",
      "content": "but it feels too specific to be just a coincidence... like, it's not just a random dream about a drink. it's the exact font, the way the light hits the can, even the specific sound of the tab cracking open. it feels way too intentional. don't you think it's weird that it's always the same brand? it almost feels like someone is trying to program my brain while I'm out.",
